I"D	<h1 id="recursion">Recursion</h1>
<p>Pastry chefs are competing to win the battle of the cakes. For each additional cake made, the number of eggs required increases by 1 (1 egg for the first cake, 2 eggs for the second, etc.).
Take the number of cakes that must be baked as the input, calculate (recursively) how many eggs were used to bake them by the end of the battle and output the result.</p>

<p>Sample Input
4</p>

<p>Sample Output
10</p>

<div class="language-cpp highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="cp">#include &lt;iostream&gt;
</span><span class="k">using</span> <span class="k">namespace</span> <span class="n">std</span><span class="p">;</span>

<span class="kt">int</span> <span class="nf">recSum</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="kt">int</span> <span class="n">n</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="p">{</span>
    <span class="c1">//complete the function</span>
    <span class="k">if</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">n</span><span class="o">==</span> <span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">){</span>
    	<span class="k">return</span> <span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">;</span>
    <span class="p">}</span>
    <span class="k">else</span><span class="p">{</span>
    	<span class="k">return</span> <span class="n">n</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="n">recSum</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">n</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">);</span>
    <span class="p">}</span>

<span class="p">}</span>

<span class="kt">int</span> <span class="nf">main</span><span class="p">()</span> <span class="p">{</span>
    <span class="c1">//getting input</span>
    <span class="kt">int</span> <span class="n">n</span><span class="p">;</span>
    <span class="n">cin</span> <span class="o">&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">n</span><span class="p">;</span>

    <span class="c1">//call the recursive function and print returned value</span>

    <span class="n">cout</span><span class="o">&lt;&lt;</span> <span class="n">recSum</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">n</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="o">&lt;&lt;</span><span class="n">endl</span><span class="p">;</span>

    <span class="k">return</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">;</span>
<span class="p">}</span>
</code></pre></div></div>
